snippet.title: The Backrooms: Found Footage | Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The Backrooms: Found Footage is a horror game that takes place in a seemingly endless maze of interconnected rooms and hallways, known as the Backrooms.
The Gameplay shown in the Trailer is subject to Change!
